&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Flodesk is one of the world’s fastest-growing email marketing companies, built to help creators sell online and design emails that people love to get. Our commitment to small business owners is to create simple and intuitive tools that help them grow, nurture, and monetize their email list.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
