&lt;p&gt;You will be joining a high-energy, global team with a clear vision: make a thriving business within reach of anyone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are already a powerhouse in the email space—serving &lt;strong&gt;thounsand verified users&lt;/strong&gt; and delivering &lt;strong&gt;1+ billion emails a month&lt;/strong&gt;. But we aren’t stopping there. We are expanding beyond email into a whole suite of marketing tool.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Backend Engineers who are problem solvers. Whether you are a strong builder (Mid-level) or a system architect (Senior), we want you to help us build high-scale infrastructure and new AI products from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do (The Mission)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will not just &quot;code tasks.&quot; You will drive business impact by working on:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High-Scale Systems:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and operate backend services that handle &lt;strong&gt;1 billion+ monthly events&lt;/strong&gt;. You will solve difficult technical challenges like speed, data processing, and stability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Innovation &amp;amp; AI:&lt;/strong&gt; Explore, utilize, and release the robust backend for an AI application to build a DIFM (Do it for me) marketing tool.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APIs &amp;amp; Integrations:&lt;/strong&gt; Design strong internal and public APIs. You will build integrations with partners like Shopify, Zapier, and WooCommerce.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; You own your code from idea to release. You will work directly with Product Managers and Designers to decide &lt;em&gt;how&lt;/em&gt; features should work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you need to be successful&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We hire for &lt;strong&gt;mindset&lt;/strong&gt; first, technology second. To succeed here, you need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Engineering Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Tech Stack:&lt;/strong&gt; We primarily use Golang and Node.js on the backend and PostgreSQL for our database. But we are open to any background (Java, Python, PHP, etc.)—we care about your logic, foundation, and problem-solving skills more than the specific language.&lt;/li&gt;
