&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System Design (For Seniors):&lt;/strong&gt; You understand how to design complex systems (Distributed systems, Databases) and can explain your choices clearly. You can design systems that stay fast even when traffic increases by 10x.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
